%% Phased Rollout Strategy Diagram
%% Illustrates the recommended approach for implementing AI code review
%% across an organization, from pilot to full-scale deployment
%%
%% Phases:
%% - Week 1: Pilot on 1-2 projects
%%   Success Metric: 60%+ developer satisfaction
%%
%% - Weeks 2-4: Team Expansion to 10-20% of teams
%%   Success Metric: <10% false positive rate
%%
%% - Month 2+: Organization-wide deployment
%%   Success Metric: Measurable velocity impact
%%
%% This progressive approach minimizes risk and allows for
%% continuous feedback and improvement
%%
%% Color Legend:
%% - Blue (#3B82F6): Pilot phase
%% - Purple (#7C3AED): Expansion phase
%% - Green (#10B981): Full deployment

graph LR
    A[Week 1:<br/>Pilot<br/>1-2 Projects] --> B[Weeks 2-4:<br/>Team Expansion<br/>10-20%]
    B --> C[Month 2+:<br/>Organization<br/>All Projects]
    
    A -.->|Metrics| A1[Developer<br/>Satisfaction<br/>60%+]
    B -.->|Metrics| B1[False Positives<br/><10%]
    C -.->|Metrics| C1[Velocity<br/>Impact<br/>Measured]
    
    style A fill:#3B82F6,color:#fff
    style B fill:#7C3AED,color:#fff
    style C fill:#10B981,color:#fff
